We have a stricken man here.

28
00:07:24,729 --> 00:07:27,107
Are you stricken, Alvin?

29
00:07:27,357 --> 00:07:30,276
Put the phone down!

30
00:07:30,527 --> 00:07:34,155
Dad, what's all the yellin'?

31
00:07:35,740 --> 00:07:38,785
Wh-what... uh,
have you done to my dad?

32
