38
00:08:33,566 --> 00:08:34,776
I'm not goin'.

39
00:08:35,026 --> 00:08:36,360
Dad.

40
00:08:36,611 --> 00:08:37,612
I'm not goin'.

41
00:08:37,862 --> 00:08:41,616
