42
00:08:55,838 --> 00:08:59,807
OK, Mr Straight,
put this robe on.

43
00:09:00,057 --> 00:09:04,019
Just bring me the doctor.

44
00:09:29,384 --> 00:09:32,971
You like birds.

45
00:09:34,097 --> 00:09:38,560
I build... uh, birdhouses...
uh, for bluebirds.

46
00:09:38,810 --> 00:09:41,271
Oh, that's nice.

47
00:09:41,521 --> 00:09:45,316
Yeah, it's Pete... uh,
Pete sells my...

48
00:09:45,567 --> 00:09:48,701
uh, birdhouses...
at the Ace Hardware.

49
00:09:48,951 --> 00:09:52,496
- I'll look for them next time.
- Yeah?

50
00:09:52,746 --> 00:09:54,832
No operation.

51
