a diabetes-related problem.

57
00:10:11,640 --> 00:10:13,815
I'd like to run some tests.

58
00:10:14,065 --> 00:10:17,068
No tests and no X-rays.

59
00:10:17,319 --> 00:10:22,115
Well, I see and hear
that you smoke.

60
00:10:22,365 --> 00:10:25,994
My guess is you're in the early
stages of emphysema.

61
00:10:26,244 --> 00:10:28,789
And Alvin,
you have circulation problems

62
00:10:29,039 --> 00:10:31,875
and I'm worried
about your diet.

63
00:10:32,125 --> 00:10:35,796
If you don't
make some changes quickly,

64
00:10:36,046 --> 00:10:40,056
there will be
some serious consequences.

65
00:11:28,700 --> 00:11:31,411
It... has a... a red roof.

66
00:11:31,661 --> 00:11:34,205
Another pretty one, Rose.

67
00:11:34,455 --> 00:11:37,584
I want to... uh,
paint the... uh, next one blue.

68
00:11:37,834 --> 00:11:41,004
That's a good idea.

69
00:11:47,385 --> 00:11:52,223
What... uh, did the doctor say?

70
00:11:53,814 --> 00:11:59,069
He said
I was gonna live to be 100.

71
00:12:33,443 --> 00:12:36,530
I think I'll go
and mow the lawn.

72
00:12:36,780 --> 00:12:39,783
Uh, I can... uh,
cut it for you, Dad.

73
00:12:40,033 --> 00:12:43,209
I got it, sweetheart.

74
00:13:17,541 --> 00:13:20,836
God darn!

75
00:13:39,694 --> 00:13:44,032
No, we'll...
we won't be mowin' today.

76
00:13:44,324 --> 00:13:47,202
