82
00:14:32,175 --> 00:14:36,638
Yeah... Yeah... Uh-huh.

83
00:14:36,888 --> 00:14:39,224
Oh, no...

84
00:14:39,474 --> 00:14:42,519
When?

85
00:14:42,644 --> 00:14:45,272
OK... right... right...

86
00:14:45,522 --> 00:14:47,232
I'll tell him.

87
00:14:47,482 --> 00:14:52,451
Yeah... OK... Bye.

88
